name: groupdocs.viewer-for-node.js-via-java
description: GroupDocs.Viewer for-Node.js-via-Java is a [Document Viewer API](https://products.groupdocs.com/viewer/java) for Java developers. It supports over 170 document types from popular categories such as Microsoft Office, OpenOffice, AutoCAD, Photoshop, Visio, images, metafiles, programming, archives, messages, PDF & more.
